        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Stop Crystal Meth Act of 2005 - Amends the Controlled Substances Act to lower the threshold quantities of mixtures or substances containing a detectable amount of methamphetamine to which penalties for controlled substances violations apply.</p>]]></text>
